description: Lists dashboards in an Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the dashboards that you're listing.

nested_items.name: DashboardSummaryList
nested_items.description: A structure that contains all of the dashboards in your Amazon Web Services account. This structure provides basic information about the dashboards.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A display name for the dashboard.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The time that this dashboard was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that this dashboard was updated.

nested_items.name: LastPublishedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that this dashboard was published.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
